sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as WorkspaceDelete
    participant Service as WorkspaceService
    participant FS as Filesystem

    User->>CLI: workspace:delete name
    alt not force and not json
        CLI->>User: confirm deletion?
        User-->>CLI: yes or no
        alt no
            CLI-->>User: cancelled
        end
    end
    CLI->>Service: delete(name)
    Service->>FS: check workspace exists
    alt not exists
        Service-->>CLI: throw RuntimeException
        CLI-->>User: error output
    else exists
        Service->>FS: deleteDirectory recursively
        Service-->>CLI: success
        CLI-->>User: success output
    end
